# EVM Hardhat ABI Tester

Use the bundle at `__BUNDLE_PATH__` when the task is to scaffold or run Hardhat tests for an existing EVM contract from ABI.

Follow this order:

1. Check `node -v` and `npm -v`
2. If either is missing, use `__BUNDLE_PATH__/references/nodejs-setup.md`
3. Read `__BUNDLE_PATH__/SKILL.md`
4. Use `__BUNDLE_PATH__/assets/hardhat-js-template/` as the canonical scaffold
5. Default all commands to `--network gsc_v2_test`
6. Prioritize read tests before write tests

Keep write tests disabled until the user confirms the contract address and transaction details.
